node.text:
I have seen several questions about the puff paint I use for my suits- it’s Tulip Dimensional Fabric Paint. Works great! Apparently you can also hit it with heat (ie hairdryer or a heat gun at low) and it’ll puff up even more. I swear I’ve tried it a zillion times to no effect 😂 but even without that it looks great!
*
*
📸 set by the incredible @thegeekstrong / @geekstrong 
*
*
Suit from Herostime with the original design by @gun_head_design 
Foam web shooter made by me ❤️
*
*
#spiderman #nowayhome #marvel #mcu #doctorstrange #puffpaint #tomholland #comics # multiverse

node.text:
“The name is Captain Carter!” 🇬🇧 So excited for my new Peggy Carter cosplay from What If…! It’s such a beautiful design ….Although the fact that the Union Jack is asymmetrical made my perfectionist brain break 😂 The breastplate is definitely my favorite part - it is heat formed worbla with foam on top. Also I love the little leather pouches I made. They’re so cute!
*
*
Gorgeous 📸 set by @thegeekstrong / @geekstrong 
*
Cosplay pieces made or modified by me!
Peggy wig from the talented @timeaftertimedesigns ❤️
*
*
#captaincarter #captainbritain #peggycarter #whatif #disneyplus #hayleyatwell ##captainamerica #cosplay #marvel #worbla #foam

Frisbee golf anyone? How about I go first!! 🛡😈 here’s a preview vid of my new Captain Carter cosplay from the upcoming What If…series on Disney+! I’m so excited with how she turned out. And you betcha I tried throwing that shield - it actually got some decent air!
*
*
Vid by @thegeekstrong / @geekstrong 
Cosplay by me!
*
*
